# /var/qmail/control/localfirstdomains
#
# Domains for which recipient resolution is "system-first": a local-part that
# names a system identity (a /home account, or an ~alias/.qmail-<name> alias)
# is delivered to that system account; everything else falls through to
# vpopmail. One domain per line. A line beginning with a dot matches subdomains.
#
# A domain listed here MUST also appear in control/rcpthosts.
#
# Example for hoth.example.org serving the example.org domain:
example.org
